# GA4 proxy — serves gtag.js and collection endpoint from own domain

/g/js https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js 200
/g/collect https://www.google-analytics.com/g/collect 200

# SPA routes — must be listed before the 404 fallback

/ /index.html 200
/partners /index.html 200

<!-- /clients       /index.html   200 -->

/articles /index.html 200
/articles/\* /index.html 200

# Everything else → 404 page with correct HTTP status

/\* /public/404.html 404
